    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive gem in pristine, showroom condition! This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and looks as if it just rolled off the assembly line, with every detail preserved to perfection. It is an absolute standout for any collector or enthusiast looking for the highest quality example available. You won't find a cleaner, more well-cared-for ride than this stunning beauty!",
      "price": 48500.0,
