    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition. This showroom-quality example has been meticulously preserved, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original luster. Every aspect of this car reflects a history of uncompromising care and preventative maintenance, ensuring it drives with the same precision and refinement as the day it left the factory. For the discerning buyer who demands the highest standard of excellence, this vehicle stands as a definitive benchmark in its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, calling this beauty 'clean' doesn't even do it justice\u2014she\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family since day one. It still has that fresh-off-the-lot feel and the drive is just incredibly smooth. You might find a microscopic pebble chip if you really go hunting, but to anyone's eye, she\u2019s practically perfect. I\u2019m really looking for a fellow enthusiast who will cherish it as much as I have. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself why I'm so head-over-heels for this ride!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines the 'Ultimate Driving Machine' ethos. This S54 powerplant is a mechanical masterpiece, recently serviced with a comprehensive Vanos overhaul using Viton seals and a full valve adjustment to ensure the timing remains razor-sharp across the entire rev range. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement to handle the increased torsional rigidity provided by the upgraded bushings. Power is transferred through a crisp six-speed manual with a rev-matched flywheel setup that eliminates lag in the torque curve. Every fluid has been analyzed for viscosity and thermal stability, ensuring the internals are as pristine as the exterior. This is a turn-key, high-compression beast optimized for the purist who demands surgical precision on every apex.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Absolute steal. First come, first served.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a time capsule of elegance and raw power. Imagine yourself carving through coastal fog as the sun dips below the horizon, the engine\u2019s low thrum harmonizing with the rhythm of the road. Every curve of its pristine silhouette tells a story of craftsmanship and prestige, while the interior welcomes you with the scent of fine leather and the promise of endless horizons. This is a rare opportunity to own a legend that looks as though it rolled off the showroom floor yesterday\u2014a masterpiece for the driver who understands that some things are truly timeless.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
